headline: RTX Corporation (RTX) Says Pratt & Whitney Strike Will Constrain Q2 Cash Flow
summary: The three-week-long strike by Pratt & Whitney engine workers is likely to weigh on RTX Corporation (NYSE:RTX)’s cash flow during the second quarter, CEO Chris Calio told the Bernstein Strategic Decisions Conference on Wednesday. On Tuesday, about 3,000 machinists approved a new four-year contract, marking the end of the first strike at the engine-maker’s Connecticut […]
